    "For example, over-relying on generative AI in coding can serve as a more immediate cyber security threat, as past versions of GitHub's Copilot were found to recommend insecure and vulnerable code to developers [81].",
    "However, few companies are prioritising must have best practises in mind, and continually revise its use.",
